verses.text:
My need is great, but greater still thy love;
Thou hast for me in all thy courts of glory;
Thy love extends to all mankind on earth;
Thy love extends to all thy throne of grace.

Thy love is now at work in me, Lord Jesus;
Thy love is now at work in me in thy mercy;
Thy love is now my counsel and my guide;
Thy love is now my strength and my defense.
